title: Albert Camus - Caligula & Three Other Plays (1962)
description:
Albert Camus - Caligula & Three Other Plays (Vintage, 1962).  Translated by Stuart Gilbert.

ISBN: 9780307827777 | 320 pages | EPUB


Four plays by Albert Camus (1913 - 1960) are included here:

  Caligula: A Play in Four Acts (1945)
  The Misunderstanding: A Play in Three Acts (1944)
  State of Siege: A Play in Three Parts (1948)
  The Just Assassins: A Play in Five Acts (1949)
